== Metadata Guidelines

=== Aliases
- Use alternative names or abbreviations
- Comma-separated list
- Think about how you might search for this note

=== Abstract
- One or two sentence summary
- Describe the main idea or purpose
- Make it searchable

=== Keywords
- Relevant topics or categories
- Use consistent terminology
- Comma-separated

